# The redirect for the renamed lead magnet (/resources/drive-home-playbook)
# used to live here because Astro's redirects: config in astro.config.mjs
# didn't fire under the old Pages-targeting Cloudflare adapter (v12). The
# Workers-targeting adapter (v13+) does honor redirects:, so it now emits
# that rule itself — keeping it here too produced a literal duplicate line
# in the generated _redirects file, which Cloudflare Workers' static-assets
# deploy validation rejects outright (Pages was more lenient about it).

# Common URLs ad networks, link checkers, and partner programs probe for.
# /privacy/ maps to our combined privacy and disclosure page.
# /terms/ is a real page now (src/pages/terms.astro). No redirect.
# /contact/ maps to /about/, where the editorial email is published.
/privacy /disclosure 301
/privacy/ /disclosure/ 301
/contact /about 301
/contact/ /about/ 301
